<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Product Catalog Service</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: white;
        }

        .container {
            margin: 0 20%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #343988;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #343988;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo {
            height: 60px;
        }

        .main {
            margin: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            text-align: left;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .centered-image {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .products-image {
            width: 70%;
            height: auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .api-link {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 0;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #343988;
            border: 2px solid #343988;
            padding: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .api-link img {
            width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .api-link h2 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .api-link:hover {
            background-color: #fea934;
            border: 2px solid #fea934;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #343988;
            color: #d3d3d3;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <section class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to <span style="color: #fea934"> Product Catalog </span> Service</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="main">
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Discover a World of Products</h2>
                <p>Our Product Catalog Service provides a rich variety of products that cater to your needs.
                    Whether you're looking for the latest electronics, trendy fashion, or unique handcrafted goods,
                    you'll find it all here.</p>
                <div class="centered-image">
                    <img src="https://i.ibb.co/MNf883L/Wavy-Tech-19-Single-05.png" alt="Products"
                        class="products-image">
                </div>
                <!-- Swagger API Docs link -->
                <a href="/product-catalog/api-docs" class="api-link">
                    <h2>Explore our API :</h2>
                    <img src="https://i.ibb.co/R6vpLdB/swagger.png" alt="API Docs">
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â©2023 Product Catalog Service. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>

</html>